Yeah, so, certainly, this will
contain 0, 1, right, since--

00:09:20.730 --> 00:09:23.400 align:middle line:84%
so 0, 1, everything
between 0 and 1

00:09:23.400 --> 00:09:25.740 align:middle line:84%
should be a cluster
point of 0 and 1

00:09:25.740 --> 00:09:28.168 align:middle line:84%
because there's always
a lot of numbers.

00:09:28.168 --> 00:09:30.210 align:middle line:84%
I mean, there's a lot of
numbers between 0 and 1.

00:09:30.210 --> 00:09:44.240 align:middle line:84%
So if I draw this 0, 1,
and [? have ?] everything

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:47.930 align:middle line:84%
